1
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,120
Gentlemen.

2
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:24,640
It's Yang Gang.

3
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:26,680
Come on out.

4
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,970
Something's not right.

5
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,759
What should we do, Mr. Xiao?

6
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,020
Did we walk into a trap?

7
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:39,580
Let's wait and see.

8
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,960
This place is called Mine K26.

9
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,370
It's the gold mine I told you about.

10
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,960
I found it.

11
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,440
As for Mine K26,

12
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,840
this is the only way out.

13
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,699
I've planted bombs on both sides.

14
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,600
I have no way out.

15
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,680
I've also called the police.

16
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,340
At worst, we all die together.

17
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,800
So stop hiding.

18
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,360
Come out.

19
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,000
Let's have a proper talk. Okay?

20
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,100
Yang Gang, what are you doing?

21
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,450
Where is Jiang Xiaomei?

22
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:02,040
President Xiao, you remember Gao Shan, right?

23
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:09,440
Gao Shan. Boss Gao.

24
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:16,120
Smuggling, prostitution, and gambling.

25
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,860
He deserved to die.

26
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,400
Xie Lao'er.

27
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:29,380
President Xiao, your most loyal dog.

28
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,960
He bullied others.

29
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,240
He was greedy.

30
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,300
He deserved to die.

31
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,620
And finally, there's you.

32
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,160
Director Xiao.

33
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,290
President Xiao.

34
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,360
The local tyrant of Dayang Village.

35
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,760
You control everything.

36
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,090
You commit every crime.

37
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,120
President Xiao.

38
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,840
Have you really never felt guilty?

39
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,440
Do you know how many people you've hurt?

40
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,770
How many innocent people have you killed?

41
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,690
Jiang's father and mother.

42
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,840
Jiang Xiaomei.

43
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,960
Luo Zhengqiang.

44
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,120
And thousands more.

45
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:19,560
The villagers of Dayang Village you drove crazy.

46
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,320
So, among all these people,

47
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:24,520
you deserve to die the most.

48
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,720
Yang Gang.

49
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,740
Jiang Xiaomei isn't dead.

50
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:34,640
You need evidence to say I killed the others, okay?

51
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,600
Are you any better?

52
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,640
Didn't you steal from the mine?

53
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,840
I deserve to die, too.

54
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:45,000
I deserve to die, too.

55
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:55,240
Because I colluded with scum like you.

56
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,560
No, Yang Gang, what exactly do you want?

57
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,960
What do you want?

58
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,800
Mr. Xiao, with everything that has happened,

59
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,600
I've figured something out.

60
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,040
I couldn't understand it before,

61
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,360
but now I realize.

62
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,160
The future of Dayang Village

63
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:21,240
has nothing to do with the mine or money.

64
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,680
It has to do with you.

65
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,120
What do you mean?

66
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,380
What does it have to do with us?

67
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,010
What are you talking about?

68
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,900
Because only without you,

69
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,450
will Dayang Village have a future.

70
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,880
Don't move! Don't be rash, Yang Gang.

71
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,040
Yang Gang. Yang Gang.

72
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,320
I've handed the recorder to the police.

73
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,400
We have to trust the police,

74
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,440
trust the law.

75
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,600
I trust the law, Situ.

76
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,480
It's too late.

77
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,920
I want to atone for my sins.

78
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,480
Atone for what?

79
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,360
I want to make up for my mistakes.

80
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,720
You should go.

81
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,720
That might be an even bigger mistake.

82
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,920
I'm begging you.

83
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,560
Just go, okay?

84
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,920
Gang.

85
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,240
Gang.

86
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,480
Look at this.

87
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:29,360
It's an admission notice from the Police University.

88
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,440
I got in.

89
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:33,960
Gang.

90
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,200
I didn't let you down.

91
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,960
Stop this, Gang.

92
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,160
Wait.

93
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:24,600
Situ, thanks.

94
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,090
I'll be waiting for you.

95
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,000
Take care.

96
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,000
Qiangzi.

97
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,880
The reforms in Dayang Village have been very successful recently.

98
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,560
Shanshui Group

99
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:13,760
has also kept its promise to settle the laid-off workers.

100
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,580
Now the villagers have money.

101
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,440
Every family is building a new house.

102
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,240
That's great.

103
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,160
How about you?

104
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,680
Xiaofang and I are working in the city.

105
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,720
We'll save enough to buy a house in a few years.

106
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,960
It takes that many years to save enough?

107
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,280
You have no idea, Gang.

108
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,960
Housing prices in the city are skyrocketing.

109
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,160
We can't even keep up.

110
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,920
By the way, Gang.

111
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:40,180
What do you plan to do now that you're out?

112
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:45,180
I haven't decided yet.

113
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,480
Why don't you come to the city with me?

114
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,540
There are more opportunities there.

115
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,520
I want to stay in Dayang Village.

116
00:10:59,040 --> 00:10:59,970
That's fine too.

117
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,200
Yong.

118
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:07,640
I believe that in a few years, Dayang Village

119
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,640
will be better than the city.

120
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,360
I believe it.
